News

Sustainability Report 2018

Sustainability Report 2018

   This seventeenth edition of the report examines the main issues and
   impacts related to Hydro-Québec’s activities in Québec from January to
   December 2018. Each of its seven chapters covers a challenge to be
   addressed, a format that was adopted after consultation with
   stakeholders.

   Consult the Sustainability Report

